room_title: Escape room "The Gentleman's Den" by Escape Redding in Redding
room_description: The CIA has been working on infiltrating the secret society for years with little to show for their efforts. Fortunately, you and your team have been able to join undercover and found a small window to investigate. You have one hour to figure out who is running the society and key information about them to finally bring the society down. But beware, if you can't find the information the CIA needs your cover will be blown and all hopes to uncover the true identity of their leader will be lost forever.
